### Test OTP Endpoints

### 1. Send OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "081234567890"
}

### 2. Verify OTP (use code from step 1)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "081234567890",
  "otp_code": "123456"
}

### 3. Resend OTP
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/resend-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "081234567890"
}

### 4. Check username availability
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/check-username
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser"
}
